1.
So many choices that I could make;
So many pathways that I could take.
I know that someday I’ll make my vow;
How will I know if that time is now?
I’ve seen the blessings that come to those
Who take their stand for you.
This isn’t something somebody chose for me;
It’s something I want to do.
(CHORUS)
I want to stand up on my two feet;
I want to answer the call.
I want to have your help when I am weak;
I want to give you my all.
I want to give you my all.
